# Walkthrough: SustainaBuy Release 0.3 🚀

We have successfully finalized Phase 4 and Phase 5 of the Release 0.3 roadmap, focusing on **AI Transparency**, **Search Discovery**, and **Performance Optimization**.

## 1. AI Scanner & Heuristic Engine 🤖

The product scanner is now powered by a **Mock Heuristic Engine**, reducing analysis time to under 2 seconds for common brands while providing a transparent, step-by-step UI.

- **Real-time Progress Messages**: Users now see specific analysis steps (mapping, verification, scoring) instead of an endless spinner.
- **Transparency Badges**: Scores are now clearly labeled as **"AI-Estimated"** or **"Verified"** with distinct iconography (`Leaf` vs `ShieldCheck`).
- **Fixed Lifecycle Hang**: The "Run Life Cycle Assessment" visual loop now terminates correctly, delivering instant results.

